\"url\\": \\"https://forgeglobal.com/spacex_stock\\",\\n      \\"name\\": \\"Forge Global — SpaceX private market pricing and secondary market activity (context for pre-split secondary market transaction prices)\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\"url\\": \\"https://forgeglobal.com/insights/how-to-invest-in-spacex-pre-ipo\\",\\n      \\"name\\": \\"Forge Global Insights — How To Invest in SpaceX Pre-IPO (secondary market valuation context)\\"\\n    }\\n  ]\\n}"}',
